description:
The IP Multimedia Subsystems Program (IPMS) provides a comprehensive overview of the major concepts and processes involved in IP Multimedia Subsystems. This course will help you better understand what IPMS is, as well as knowledge and understanding of the essential components. The book supports the eLearning content and provides a further analysis of each of the relevant areas.

This program prepares you for the IPMS exam, providing you with information and useful examples related to the use of IPMS Technologies.
title: IP Multimedia
